TO MICHAEL…

Wow….. 13yrs you’ve been in my life. Such a protector of me even when I just want you to be a kid. We’ve basically grown up together son and I’m just so happy you were assigned to me ❤️🫶🏾 You’re really my best friend. I don’t hide anything from you, when no one is there you are there to tell me everything is gonna be okay. It’s been like that 13yrs now. You’ve been a BIG BROTHER and had to share me since you were 18months and never complain. You understand my hustle. You are so patient with me. Such a humble kid… we’ve been bumping heads lately but it’s because you’re growing up and I understand after yesterday more than ever after sitting down and talking to you…. I HAVE TO LET YOU DO THAT. 

I know God gave you a drill sergeant for a mother but in due time when you become the hard working man, father and husband you will be, I’m sure you’ll thank me cause one thing I’m not doing is letting up off you King 👑❤️🫶🏾

I couldn’t post yesterday because I was so busy spending time, intimate time with you but you changed my life for the better Kiddo! I owe you the world be patient, I’ma give it to you ❤️ Welcome to your teenage years son Mommy loves you! We gonna forever be each other’s BIGGEST STEPPERS for life 🥹🫶🏾❤️

Fine like wine… 🍷 I’ll just keep getting better with time 🕰

When I say I’ve learned my purpose… my whole life I’ve had a light in me 💯 I never knew what it was until I decided to drop all distractions, move from back home and start my life completely OVER from the bottom at 30 in a new place. Throughout my journey it’s been revealed to me (sometimes when God reveals things he makes you go through things to learn lessons that turn into blessings) but back on track… it’s been revealed to me that I’m put here as an example of self love.

I LOVE THE FUCK OUT OF MYSELF! To people who see my confidence as an issue it’s because they haven’t reached their era of full self love that’s why No matter where I meet people I am kind to them. I uplift them… and I tell them what I see in them because sometimes people don’t see the light in themselves. Everyone has an inner light and I like to think of my purpose as just being a vessel to make people feel good about themselves.

I’ve always loved myself but I did it all wrong… loving yourself is even when you are going through things keeping yourself encouraged. I meet people from all walks of life from rich people to homeless people and I treat them all the same. I am kind to them and I encourage everyone to do the same…. The world would be such a nicer place 🫶🏾❤️

The people who truly know me and my story would say I’m an inspiration because I will never look like what I been through 🥹🫶🏾 or act like what I’ve been through 💯

The purpose of this photo shoot for me is because I’ve never been in front of a camera for a photo shoot like this but I wake up and THANK GOD EVERYDAY for choosing me to be Ja’Miecia out of all of the people he could have made me I’m honored to be me. I want to share this song with my followers who may be experiencing weariness or may be down been listening to it 22yrs Since I was 10 and discovered who @indiaarie was! She made this song and it’s forever been a part of me throughout my last 22yrs of life… when I was younger and people told me I looked like her I hated it but as a 32 year old woman I’d never want to look any other way. 

If y’all ever need some self love inspiration play this song. BE YOU, LOVE YOURSELF, BE KIND. That’s all! HBD to me ❤️

Everyone has that one child of theirs that they just know is KARMA 😭😂

One thing about my Karma is his greatness out weighs his middle child syndrome. OUT OF ALL 3 OF MY SONS, Ashton is the most like me! I mean he is me and I am him literally 💯 His demeanor, the way he loves to look nice, the way he not going for shit 💯🤞🏾😴, the way he is always the smallest person in the room, but will forever have the biggest presence. His musical talent, performance abilities. His heart is so pure and that’s why he puts so emotion into everything he does….

The way he makes sure he hugs me and tells me he love me everyday🥹
And tell me I look fire 🔥 when I’m about to walk out the house all dolled up!

The ladies love AJ and that’s that charm…. Cause one thing we gonna do is let our laws of attraction play out…. I MEAN NAME A BETTER MOM SON DUO… that’s how we feel about us together 😂🤞🏾

WHO DOES HE SOUND LIKE…. WHO DOES HE LOOK LIKE? ME‼️ My second son and I bump heads so damn much because I be trying to teach him things I didn’t realize about myself until my late 20s but one thing I’m going to promise to do is sew into every talent my baby has! 

I MADE THE DECISION ABOUT 60DAYS AGO SECRETLY TO STOP DOING MUSIC 🎵 that’s because everything I’ve learned and all of my knowledge I’m putting into my twin! I can’t wait for y’all to see his journey…. Today he is 12‼️ At 13 he’s going to drop his first EP and I promised him today for the next year to mold him and put him in front of every door that I’ve turned down this last year and a half in Atlanta. I’ve been going around networking knowing I’m done with music but every door I have walked in has heard about Ashton‼️🫶🏾 

My baby is a Star and we manifest that…. SLIDE TO THE LAST SLIDE… that’s me and my twin 5-10yrs from now ❤️😮‍💨

I love you Ashton James Corbin! Sky is the limit for us and Happy 12th bday twinnem 🥹🫣😮‍💨🫶🏾 You that guy fr fr 🔥🔥🔥

GM friends and family 🫶🏾

As you all know I accepted a position as a on-site director at Simply The Best Academy in Lithonia, GA last month and I just wanted to start by saying we are one HUGE family. My child has been at this school over a year before I accepted the position so these parents and students mean so much to me!

I’m writing this post because one of my staff members she’s Mitchell’s daytime teacher (she’s an Ohio girl too) and her youngest son were a victim of a drive by shooting Monday night about 2 hrs after she clocked out of work. 

She was breastfeeding her youngest son Tristian whose our youngest baby at the school (7 months) when bullets flew through her window grazing her. But unfortunately baby Tristian was struck in the head and in the shoulder. Yesterday in surgery they were able to remove the bullet from his shoulder, unfortunately not the one in his head 😢 in the midst of all of this she now has to find a new place while in the hospital with her baby fighting and we’ve all come together to raise awareness to get them help. Her older two sons (elementary age were there as well) but by gods grace didn’t get hit. Her mental can’t allow her to even think right now but she has a work family and close friends who are here for her‼️

We are organizing and sharing this GoFundMe because this baby has a long road to recovery ❤️‍🩹 He is such a fighter! His first surgery was very successful on the up side of things. In the mean time we are asking that if you can please donate to help her. Another coworker and I have found her a nice townhome to relocate but with her not being able to work until further notice, she’s going to need a lot of assistance! This is an extremely sad situation so close to the holidays and she’s worried about her baby first and foremost but also not having a place to return to! 

Our goal is for when baby Tristian is finally able to return home he will have a nice place to come, her kids will be able to experience a good holiday season and she will have enough funds to help her not worry about finances and be able to focus on her sons long recovery ahead! 

If any of you can help, #LinkInBio #TristianStrong ❤️‍🩹🧸
